text: Gelato flavours are unique but the taste was not impressive...a bit overpriced considering its location. With this price range I would probably not going back again
Latte is nice. I can smell it when walk pass. Gelato has many different unique flavor. Good.

A really quiet and "inside" place that is incredibly comfortable. You'll probably have to drive or get a ride to get there though. Nice ice cream flavors, and an interesting experience when paired with their mochi waffle. The staff there are very friendly and helpful, the ambience is pleasant and inviting. The place has both indoor and outdoor seating, so you can choose whichever suits your fancy.

mochi waffles with canadian maple syrup is very Q and crispy. gelato flavours are unique and interesting. There is a coffee stand here too, but it opens till 6pm. We were there at night. I also saw some beer. Will come back in the near future for coffee.
Very chill cafe with nice outdoor seating area (nice and cooling especially on rainy days). Great coffee with non dairy alternatives and there's also interesting ice cream flavors with waffles.
